This kit is designed to provide an out-of-the-box experience for working with AWS CloudTrail logs.

It provides the following utilities:
- Queries
- Detections
- Stats
- Dashboards
- Actionables
- Templates

Refer to playbooks for implementation guides, and a kit overview for more detail on components.

